ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions

Class CumulativeProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.cep.Processor
      • ca.uqac.lif.cep.SingleProcessor
        • ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions.FunctionProcessor
          • ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions.CumulativeProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contextualizable, Cloneable

    public class CumulativeProcessor
extends FunctionProcessor
    Creates a cumulative processor out of a cumulative function. This is simply a FunctionProcessor whose function is of a specific type (a CumulativeFunction). However, it has a special grammar that allows any binary function to be turned into a cumulative processor.
